  "How many independent equations does Kirchhoff's junction rule provide for a circuit with N junctions?": "",
  "2N": "",
  "N + 1": "",
  "N": "",
  "N - 1": "",
  "For N junctions, only N - 1 independent equations can be obtained from the junction rule. The Nth equation is linearly dependent on the others.": "",
  "In a closed loop with a 12 V battery and two resistors (4 ohm and 2 ohm in series), what is the current?": "",
  "6 A": "",
  "2 A": "",
  "1 A": "",
  "3 A": "",
  "By Kirchhoff's loop rule: 12 V - I(4) - I(2) = 0, so 12 = 6I, giving I = 2 A.": "",
